{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cardalaxy is a <strong>card upgrading</strong> game with <strong>4X inspiration</strong> and <br><i><strong>5+ different victories</strong>.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This demo contains the first playable faction with the 5 base systems - Production, Defense, Wellness, Science, and Exploration.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The full game will contain additional factions who each have a different mix of systems.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Upgrade Planets</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Upgrade your planets with buildings to increase their value. Advance through multiple tiers of buildings, each with better effects and bonuses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3472050/extras/Planet_Upgrading.gif?t=1737749038\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Research, Explore, Develop</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect points and use them in each of the different systems to advance your empire. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3472050/extras/Tech_Tree.gif?t=1737749038\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Defend your Empire</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enemies are constantly threatening the empire. Collect defense and use it to fight them off.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3472050/extras/Combat.gif?t=1737749038\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Achieve Victory!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose your path to victory - Production, Defense, Wellness, Science, or Exploration. Each has a unique way to win.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3472050/extras/Victory.gif?t=1737749038\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3472050/page_bg_generate